Known cases of Covid-19 are concentrated highest in London, particularly Brent, Southwark and Lambeth.

The Aneurin Bevan Health Board (covers Newport, Caerphilly, Monmouthshire) has recorded over 1,000 cases.

Take this as mostly a reflection of testing.
